OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,FDigital prescriptions are to be rolled
OL,7,Fout across Northern Ireland, paid for
OL,8,Fby a fund given to Stormont to
OL,9,Ftransform public services.
OL,11,FThe Finance Minister announced on
OL,12,FTuesday that several departments will
OL,13,Fshare a #102.6 million funding pot to
OL,14,Fmake services more efficient.
OL,16,FIt comes after UTV revealed in April
OL,17,Fthat the vast majority of a
OL,18,F#230million funding pot given to
OL,19,FStormont two years ago to transform
OL,20,Fpublic services wasn't spent.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
