PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779970272
OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,FThe other allocations include #29.2
OL,7,Fmillion for the Together for Families
OL,8,Fproject, a partnership to establish a
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland-wide model to ensure
OL,10,Ffamilies can access the help they
OL,11,Fneed, and #16 million for a Pathways
OL,12,Fto Work and Wellbeing proposal to
OL,13,Fsupport more people with ill-health
OL,14,Fand disabilities to enter and remain
OL,15,Fin employment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779970272
OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,FMeanwhile, #6 million was allocated
OL,7,Ffor a digital workplace programme to
OL,8,Fmodernise records and information
OL,9,Fmanagement across the Civil Service,
OL,10,F#5.3 million for a data linkage office
OL,11,Fto deliver two pathfinder projects to
OL,12,Fexamine the capability to safely link
OL,13,Fdata across departments and #4 million
OL,14,Ffor a bovine tuberculosis research
OL,15,Fproject.
OL,17,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd said the
OL,18,Ftransformation of public services aims
OL,19,Fto make them more effective and
OL,20,Fsustainable.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
