PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779970272
OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,F"The Executive is committed to
OL,7,Fchanging how we deliver services to
OL,8,Fimprove lives, strengthen communities
OL,9,Fand achieve better outcomes," he said.
OL,11,F"At its heart, transformation is about
OL,12,Fworking differently to make services
OL,13,Fmore effective, resilient and
OL,14,Fsustainable, especially in a time of
OL,15,Fconstrained public finances."
OL,17,FMr O'Dowd said last year he announced
OL,18,F#129 million from the Transformation
OL,19,FFund for six public sector projects
OL,20,Facross healthcare, special educational
OL,21,Fneeds, justice and infrastructure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]sD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779970272
OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,F"I am now pleased to announce the
OL,7,Fsecond tranche of funding and a
OL,8,Ffurther #102.6 million, for an
OL,9,Fadditional six projects to support the
OL,10,Fcontinued transformation of our
OL,11,Fservices. This is complemented by a
OL,12,Ffurther #30 million from the National
OL,13,FLottery community fund and #5.6
OL,14,Fmillion from the Shared Island Fund,"
OL,15,Fhe added.
OL,17,F"The Transformation Fund is a key step
OL,18,Fin improving public services and
OL,19,Fdelivering the reforms people need and
OL,20,Fdeserve.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@eO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779970272
OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,F"This investment will not only deliver
OL,7,Fgreater efficiency and long-term
OL,8,Fsavings across government, but will
OL,9,Falso strengthen healthcare, support
OL,10,Ffamilies, help our farmers and the
OL,11,Fagri-food sector, and lay the
OL,12,Fgroundwork for bold, system-wide
OL,13,Fchange in the years ahead."
OL,15,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt welcomed
OL,16,Fthe funding.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
