PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779970272
OL,3,C'E-pharmacy' among Stormont projects
OL,4,Cto benefit from #100m fund
OL,6,FHe said: "With over 45 million items
OL,7,Fprescribed and dispensed annually
OL,8,Facross primary care in Northern
OL,9,FIreland, transitioning from paper
OL,10,Fprescriptions to a digital system will
OL,11,Fgenuinely transform patient experience.
OL,13,F"This project and the new digital
OL,14,Fplatform will help to make health and
OL,15,Fsocial care as safe as possible,
OL,16,Faccelerate primary care reform and
OL,17,Fhelp support our move towards a
OL,18,Fneighbourhood model of care for
OL,19,Fprimary, community and social care."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU{D@dO]
